Description: fix 64 bit portability
  * src/cg_music.c: Fixed pointer cast where a 'long' (8 bytes on x86_64) was 
    treated as an 'unsigned int' (4 bytes), causing truncated reads of the 
    music rate. 
  * src/shader.c: Fixed potential truncation when handling large shader files. 
